{
  "texts": [
    "CodeTailor can be adapted to support these activities by simply changing the content.",
    "This work has several limitations.",
    "(1) The user study is a small-scale think-aloud study; it was not conducted in a real educational setting where students might behave differently with different preferences.",
    "(2) The effect of CodeTailor on students' long-term knowledge retention and far-transfer learning is still unclear.",
    "(3) Limited feedback on the quality of LLM-produced Parsons distractors due to few falling into this personalization scenario."
  ]
}